{"tid":1890290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我懷疑Youtube刪黃圈youtuber訂閲！","createTime":"2020-02-21T06:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T12:12:09.000Z","uid":311057,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c77e523b9409b7b2faac195d74140b43cc4907","tid":1890290,"uid":311057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:06:37.000Z","msg":"事緣我見有位巴打好有心，佢公開咗自己嘅訂閱項目，<br />\n入面全部都係黃色YouTuber, 咁我入去訂閲啦，<br />\n之後發現入邊啲訂閱數目係會又升又跌，<br />\n前一秒上十幾個，下一秒又跌返，<br />\n我懷疑因為我哋一次過訂閱太多YouTube Channel嘅時候冇睇佢哋嘅片，之後Youtube就刪咗啲訂閲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以可能要睇一睇啲片先再訂閲, 或者睇吓大家有冇其他解決方法<br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 繼續入去訂閲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgTB9TyofzQWNnJ7M-QLfDQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCgTB9TyofzQWNnJ7M-QLfDQ&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=73a4ad2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgTB9TyofzQWNnJ7M-QLfDQ</a>"},{"pid":"d844121a7522c068a6a5afceb816196a20b05967","tid":1890290,"uid":293619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"34a69c4c261ce010e9b29239cccd2f4a53fab61e","tid":1890290,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"訂閱完。要入去play下片、like 同comment"},{"pid":"e6f6c46fc62e61b38eaba8c25c80d68c7b297104","tid":1890290,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0c4938068f6bcabe244871d2b74db3c092570ca","tid":1890290,"uid":311057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"所以大家訂閱嘅同時，都入去睇一睇佢哋啲片先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdb66b34b5097cbd323f0f6d7866c41ff9d57a2","tid":1890290,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"我地小隊依家正努力整合緊屬於我地香港本土YouTube channel<im